abstract: Manchester United defeats Crystal Palace, 2-1, in extra time, winning 135th Football Assn Cup; other soccer scores noted.
lead_paragraph: The longtime powerhouse salvaged its season by winning its first trophy since Alex Ferguson retired.

headline.main: Manchester United Ends Trophy Drought by Winning the F.A. Cup
headline.print_headline: United Ends Trophy Drought and Disappointing Season With F.A. Cup Victory

snippet: The longtime powerhouse salvaged its season by winning its first trophy since Alex Ferguson retired.
